---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, "");
const photo = `${base}/images/owais.jpg`;
---
<Layout
  title="About — The Madinah Way"
  description="About Owais Akbani — software engineer and Aalim-e-Deen behind The Madinah Way."
>
  <section class="mb-10">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">
      About<span class="text-emerald-400">.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">The story behind The Madinah Way.</p>
  </section>

  <article class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 sm:grid-cols-[auto,1fr] sm:items-start">
    <figure class="mx-auto sm:mx-0">
      <img
        src={photo}
        alt="Owais Akbani"
        width="220"
        height="220"
        class="h-44 w-44 rounded-full object-cover shadow-lg ring-4 ring-emerald-100 sm:h-56 sm:w-56"
        loading="eager"
      />
      <figcaption class="mt-3 text-center text-sm text-slate-600">Owais Akbani</figcaption>
    </figure>

    <div class="prose-about">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Assalāmu ʿalaykum 👋</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
        I'm <strong>Owais Akbani</strong> — a seasoned <em>Software Engineer</em> and an
        <em>Aalim-e-Deen</em> who studied Islam in the classical way. I am a
        <strong>Hanafi</strong> in fiqh and follow the
        <strong>Naqshbandi</strong> school of Sufism.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
        <strong>The Madinah Way</strong> is my attempt to bring the two worlds I love together —
        the timeless tradition of Islamic learning and the clarity of modern, interactive tools.
        The goal is simple: make authentic Islamic knowledge easier to engage with, one card,
        one lesson, one idea at a time.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
        Whether you're learning Arabic, or revisiting the
        fundamentals of <em>ʿaqīdah</em> and <em>fiqh</em>, I hope something here helps you on
        your path.
      </p>

      <h3 class="mt-8 text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">Connect</h3>
      <ul class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://www.youtube.com/c/OwaisAkbani"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-slate-300 bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800 transition hover:border-emerald-500 hover:text-emerald-700"
          >
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="h-4 w-4" aria-hidden="true" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M23.5 6.2a3 3 0 0 0-2.1-2.1C19.6 3.6 12 3.6 12 3.6s-7.6 0-9.4.5A3 3 0 0 0 .5 6.2 31 31 0 0 0 0 12a31 31 0 0 0 .5 5.8 3 3 0 0 0 2.1 2.1c1.8.5 9.4.5 9.4.5s7.6 0 9.4-.5a3 3 0 0 0 2.1-2.1c.4-1.9.5-3.8.5-5.8s-.1-3.9-.5-5.8zM9.6 15.6V8.4l6.4 3.6-6.4 3.6z"/>
            </svg>
            YouTube
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/owaisakbani/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-slate-300 bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800 transition hover:border-emerald-500 hover:text-emerald-700"
          >
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="h-4 w-4" aria-hidden="true" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M20.45 20.45h-3.55v-5.57c0-1.33-.02-3.04-1.86-3.04-1.86 0-2.15 1.45-2.15 2.95v5.66H9.34V9h3.41v1.56h.05c.48-.9 1.65-1.86 3.39-1.86 3.62 0 4.29 2.39 4.29 5.49v6.26zM5.34 7.43a2.06 2.06 0 1 1 0-4.12 2.06 2.06 0 0 1 0 4.12zM7.12 20.45H3.56V9h3.56v11.45zM22.23 0H1.77C.79 0 0 .77 0 1.72v20.56C0 23.23.79 24 1.77 24h20.46c.98 0 1.77-.77 1.77-1.72V1.72C24 .77 23.21 0 22.23 0z"/>
            </svg>
            LinkedIn
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
